IDInterface
public class NegotiationItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDInterface

A NegotiationItem acts as a container, which has a Negotiation, a NegotiationIssue and a arbitrary number of Offers. Further it is a CommunicationItem, so Actors are able to talk about NegotiationItems
